---
/**
 * Tiny inline-SVG icon component.
 *
 * Each entry in ICONS pairs a viewBox with a `body` of raw inner SVG markup,
 * exported from Figma or copied from Iconify. Using raw markup (rather than a
 * single `path` string) lets us support stroked icons, grouped paths, circles,
 * and any other primitives without growing the API.
 *
 * Sizing is via the standard Tailwind size-* utilities passed through `class`,
 * defaulting to size-5 (20px) to match the Figma design system. Colour follows
 * currentColor so it inherits from the parent (e.g. button text) — unless the
 * icon is flagged as `multicolor`, in which case the inner paths' own fills win.
 *
 * Stroked icons (e.g. `slack`, `github`) embed their own `fill="none" stroke=…`
 * attributes, so the wrapping <svg> stays neutral and they paint correctly.
 */
